name: acousticness
desc: A measure from 0.0 to 1.0 of whether the track is acoustic.

name: loudness
desc: The overall loudness of a track in decibels (dB). Loudness values are averaged across the entire track. Values typical range between -60 and 0 db.

name: tempo
desc: The overall estimated tempo of a track in beats per minute (BPM). In musical terminology, tempo is the speed or pace of a given piece and derives directly from the average beat duration.
